videos.headline: Army caps epic opening drive on Woolfolk TD
videos.description: Darnell Woolfolk caps Army's nearly 13-minute opening drive with a 1-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Hopkins sneaks into the end zone to extend Army's lead
videos.description: Kelvin Hopkins Jr. gives Army a 14-0 lead over Air Force with a 6-yard touchdown run.
